data.description: Motivated Seller! Beautiful home in Leawood Lakes Community , 3/2.5 offering this loving home! This home offers open floor plan conveying an inviting, welcoming ambiance to family and guests. This spacious and open, fully equipped island kitchen and dinning room. . Owners suite is located on first floor and offers 2 closets with a large bathroom, dual sinks, sepearte tub/shower, and the view of the lake. The laundry is located on the first floor and has space for storage, extra closet downstairs,  across laundry room there's half bathroom, and a door for outside access.  Upstairs you have 2 spacious rooms with large closet and a guest bathroom.This community features extra parking and  for pool area. Minutes  from Tin City, Downtown Naples, I-75 and Golden Gate Parkway, Commercial area and much more, come see!!!!!  New roof 2022.
